SAM (Segment Anything Model) Models

1. SAM

- B:  Fast, low VRAM (≤12GB)
- L:  Balanced (16–24GB)
- H: Best quality, high VRAM (face/hair/skin)

B, L, H - Base, Large, and Huge

2. SAM2

Faster, better masks, more efficient than SAM v1. Ideal all-rounder.

3. BiSeNet

Lightweight, very fast, good for real-time tasks, but lower mask quality.

BBOX (Segment Anything Model)

- face_yolov9c.pt – best accuracy for faces, recommended
- face_yolov8m.pt – slightly less accurate, still good
- hand_yolov9c.pt – best for hand detection, precise
- hand_yolov8s.pt – lighter, slightly less accurate

Note on model sizes:

n = nano (very fast, least accurate)
s = small (fast, decent accuracy)
m = medium (good balance)
c = compact (YOLOv9 only, efficient and accurate)
l = large (more accurate, slower)
x = extra large (most accurate, slowest)
